: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">课程大纲</p></section></section></section></section></section><section style="margin: -3px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0px 0px -3px; padding: 0px; width: 6px; height: 6px; float: left; background-color: rgb(237, 161, 60); border-radius: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="margin: 0px -3px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; width: 6px; height: 6px; float: right; background-color: rgb(237, 161, 60); border-radius: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">清晰传递信息：短时间内快速组织信息并有效传递</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【设计标题】：设计一个吸引读者眼球的标题</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【撰写序言】：写一段让读者愿意看下去的精彩开头</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【展开内容】：快速构建职场常见场景下的行文脉络<br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">准确总结工作：写一份有思想有高度的工作总结</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【要素归类】：找到为自己加分的关键工作过程和成果</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【总结概括】：将自己的工作业绩写出高度</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【排序整理】：让工作总结变得一目了然</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">充分说服他人：观点明确、有理有据地进行职场说服</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【明确观点】：说服他人的前提是一个鲜明的观点</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【需求分析】：what’s in it for you</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【疑问回答】：用充分地依据回答读者心中的疑问</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【逻辑归整】：用逻辑论证使说服更有力量</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">有力汇报方案：写出有价值有力度的方案</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【描述问题定方向】：挖掘需求锁定写作方向</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【基于目标定主题】：以终为始紧盯方案目标</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【纵向结构分层次】：换位思考解答对方困惑</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【横向结构选顺序】：梳理逻辑厘清表达思路</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【形象表达做演示】：深入浅出传递关键信息</span></p>

4-3 纵向结构分层次

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/app9lltoYxm7260/v_5a530400cc81a_BIbaXt7O

<section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">记得么？我们小时候花很多年去练习写记叙文、说明文和议论文。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">然鹅！这些文体我们在工作中却很少用到！！！</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appAUaBYivz8405/image/ueditor/57575700_1515389826.cn/mmbiz_jpg/hcphm4dmbzjmbqqignv4qrntxqur9r7vciuzifxxgtlxn6cj8g3tqviaozjicgc1ciaic5ssjasgqeicsl2ctvkghda/0" title="http://7xo6kd.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/upload-ueditor-image-20170325-1490424733170078614.jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">多数时候，我们要写一段文字，目的并不是为了记录什么、说明什么、议论什么，而是为了去说服别人！</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">尤其在职场中，比如：说服领导采纳自己的建议，说服顾客购买自己的产品，甚至是说服老板给自己加薪...&nbsp;<br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appAUaBYivz8405/image/ueditor/74441500_1515389826.cn/mmbiz_jpg/hcphm4dmbzjmbqqignv4qrntxqur9r7vndib71qiccv1slaicxwzspczjvtpd1krmc0zf26mjwlbcwwyvr2wn68aw/0" title="http://7xo6kd.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/upload-ueditor-image-20170325-1490424756104065609.jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"/></span><br/></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 1px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">这种“以说服别人为目的”的写作就叫做<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);">“说服性写作”</span>。</strong></section><br/></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0.5em 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appAUaBYivz8405/image/ueditor/85755500_1515389826.cn/mmbiz_gif/hcphm4dmbzlojyprtoicwffbimpay3t2uv0dtmfympj9u7zavc1tdjgdfqo6ccicibdbqfbsib6mw91jfyj6bf1eq/0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important;"/></section></section></section></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">对大多数人来说，这是最有用、使用频率最高的一种文体。<br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">说服性写作和议论文有点像，但～绝～对～不～是～一回事儿。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">举个栗子：&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">1-议论文侧重点在“我”：</span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">我的观点是什么、为什么我有这样的观点；</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">我喜欢养宠物，是因为……</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">2-说服性写作侧重点在“读者”：</span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">内容是关注读者点立场和观点，从对方的角度出发，考虑怎么能让对方认同我的观点。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">建议你养个宠物，它可以…它可以…它可以…</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">如此看来，我们一生中做的大部分努力，其实都是在说服别人！</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">申请一个职位、汇报一个方案、总结一项工作，甚至写一封邮件，其实都是在做说服性写作。&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">可素！！！</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">从小到大，我们接受的所有写作方法中，却基本没教过如何写“说服性文字”！</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">如何轻松写出观点清晰、结构严谨、逻辑缜密的文字，并成功说服对方呢？</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">结构思考力学院线上学习平台“杏壳”重新整合，率先推出<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0); font-size: 16px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">升级版善写训练营</strong></span>，这大概是你能找到的最实用的“说服性写作”课程！</span></p><p><br/></p><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px 3px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 3px 0px 0px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(237, 161, 60); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(237, 161, 60); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: -3px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0px 0px -1px; padding: 0px; width: 6px; height: 6px; float: left; border-radius: 100%; background-color: rgb(237, 161, 60); box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="margin: 0px -1px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; width: 6px; height: 6px; float: right; border-radius: 100%; background-color: rgb(237, 161, 60); box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 8px 10px 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">不一样的写作课</p></section></section></section></section></section><section style="margin: -3px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0px 0px -3px; padding: 0px; width: 6px; height: 6px; float: left; background-color: rgb(237, 161, 60); border-radius: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">我们不讲</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">如何写出10万+的微信爆文，只教你如何成为老板想要的人</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">我们不讲</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">如何靠写作日入5万的浮夸，只教你如何用职场写作倍受客户认可</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">我们不讲</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">如何从0开始做到妙笔生花，只教你如何轻松完成工作汇报不再一筹莫展</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">我们不讲……</span></p><p><br/></p><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px 3px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 3px 0px 0px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(237, 161, 60); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(237, 161, 60); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: -3px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0px 0px -1px; padding: 0px; width: 6px; height: 6px; float: left; border-radius: 100%; background-color: rgb(237, 161, 60); box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="margin: 0px -1px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; width: 6px; height: 6px; float: right; border-radius: 100%; background-color: rgb(237, 161, 60); box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 8px 10px 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">讲师介绍</p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appAUaBYivz8405/image/ueditor/416900_1515389827.png" title=".png" alt="image.png" style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">李忠秋 讲师<br/></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">结构思考力学院创始人</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">北京思考力管理咨询有限公司总裁</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">为众多500强企业提供过结构思考力的企业培训，覆盖包括企业中高层管理者、骨干员工等上万名学员，是国内该领域内最有影响力的研究、实践与推广者。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">著《结构思考力》《透过结构看世界》等。</span></p><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px 3px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 3px 0px 0px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(237, 161, 60); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(237, 161, 60); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: -3px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0px 0px -1px; padding: 0px; width: 6px; height: 6px; float: left; border-radius: 100%; background-color: rgb(237, 161, 60); box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="margin: 0px -1px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; width: 6px; height: 6px; float: right; border-radius: 100%; background-color: rgb(237, 161, 60); box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 8px 10px 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">课程大纲</p></section></section></section></section></section><section style="margin: -3px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0px 0px -3px; padding: 0px; width: 6px; height: 6px; float: left; background-color: rgb(237, 161, 60); border-radius: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="margin: 0px -3px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; width: 6px; height: 6px; float: right; background-color: rgb(237, 161, 60); border-radius: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">清晰传递信息：短时间内快速组织信息并有效传递</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【设计标题】：设计一个吸引读者眼球的标题</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【撰写序言】：写一段让读者愿意看下去的精彩开头</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【展开内容】：快速构建职场常见场景下的行文脉络<br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">准确总结工作：写一份有思想有高度的工作总结</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【要素归类】：找到为自己加分的关键工作过程和成果</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【总结概括】：将自己的工作业绩写出高度</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【排序整理】：让工作总结变得一目了然</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">充分说服他人：观点明确、有理有据地进行职场说服</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【明确观点】：说服他人的前提是一个鲜明的观点</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【需求分析】：what’s in it for you</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【疑问回答】：用充分地依据回答读者心中的疑问</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【逻辑归整】：用逻辑论证使说服更有力量</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">有力汇报方案：写出有价值有力度的方案</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【描述问题定方向】：挖掘需求锁定写作方向</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【基于目标定主题】：以终为始紧盯方案目标</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【纵向结构分层次】：换位思考解答对方困惑</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【横向结构选顺序】：梳理逻辑厘清表达思路</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【形象表达做演示】：深入浅出传递关键信息</span></p>

4-2 基于目标定主题

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/app9He58bHl9078/v_5a530400cc7cd_QqZQh2T1

<section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">记得么？我们小时候花很多年去练习写记叙文、说明文和议论文。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">然鹅！这些文体我们在工作中却很少用到！！！</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appAUaBYivz8405/image/ueditor/57575700_1515389826.cn/mmbiz_jpg/hcphm4dmbzjmbqqignv4qrntxqur9r7vciuzifxxgtlxn6cj8g3tqviaozjicgc1ciaic5ssjasgqeicsl2ctvkghda/0" title="http://7xo6kd.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/upload-ueditor-image-20170325-1490424733170078614.jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">多数时候，我们要写一段文字，目的并不是为了记录什么、说明什么、议论什么，而是为了去说服别人！</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">尤其在职场中，比如：说服领导采纳自己的建议，说服顾客购买自己的产品，甚至是说服老板给自己加薪...&nbsp;<br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appAUaBYivz8405/image/ueditor/74441500_1515389826.cn/mmbiz_jpg/hcphm4dmbzjmbqqignv4qrntxqur9r7vndib71qiccv1slaicxwzspczjvtpd1krmc0zf26mjwlbcwwyvr2wn68aw/0" title="http://7xo6kd.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/upload-ueditor-image-20170325-1490424756104065609.jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"/></span><br/></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 1px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">这种“以说服别人为目的”的写作就叫做<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);">“说服性写作”</span>。</strong></section><br/></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0.5em 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appAUaBYivz8405/image/ueditor/85755500_1515389826.cn/mmbiz_gif/hcphm4dmbzlojyprtoicwffbimpay3t2uv0dtmfympj9u7zavc1tdjgdfqo6ccicibdbqfbsib6mw91jfyj6bf1eq/0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important;"/></section></section></section></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">对大多数人来说，这是最有用、使用频率最高的一种文体。<br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">说服性写作和议论文有点像，但～绝～对～不～是～一回事儿。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">举个栗子：&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">1-议论文侧重点在“我”：</span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">我的观点是什么、为什么我有这样的观点；</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">我喜欢养宠物，是因为……</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">2-说服性写作侧重点在“读者”：</span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">内容是关注读者点立场和观点，从对方的角度出发，考虑怎么能让对方认同我的观点。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">建议你养个宠物，它可以…它可以…它可以…</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">如此看来，我们一生中做的大部分努力，其实都是在说服别人！</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">申请一个职位、汇报一个方案、总结一项工作，甚至写一封邮件，其实都是在做说服性写作。&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">可素！！！</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">从小到大，我们接受的所有写作方法中，却基本没教过如何写“说服性文字”！</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">如何轻松写出观点清晰、结构严谨、逻辑缜密的文字，并成功说服对方呢？</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">结构思考力学院线上学习平台“杏壳”重新整合，率先推出<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0); font-size: 16px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">升级版善写训练营</strong></span>，这大概是你能找到的最实用的“说服性写作”课程！</span></p><p><br/></p><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px 3px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 3px 0px 0px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(237, 161, 60); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(237, 161, 60); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: -3px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0px 0px -1px; padding: 0px; width: 6px; height: 6px; float: left; border-radius: 100%; background-color: rgb(237, 161, 60); box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="margin: 0px -1px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; width: 6px; height: 6px; float: right; border-radius: 100%; background-color: rgb(237, 161, 60); box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 8px 10px 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">不一样的写作课</p></section></section></section></section></section><section style="margin: -3px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0px 0px -3px; padding: 0px; width: 6px; height: 6px; float: left; background-co