px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【要素归类】：找到为自己加分的关键工作过程和成果</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【总结概括】：将自己的工作业绩写出高度</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【排序整理】：让工作总结变得一目了然</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">充分说服他人：观点明确、有理有据地进行职场说服</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【明确观点】：说服他人的前提是一个鲜明的观点</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【需求分析】：what’s in it for you</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【疑问回答】：用充分地依据回答读者心中的疑问</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【逻辑归整】：用逻辑论证使说服更有力量</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">有力汇报方案：写出有价值有力度的方案</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【描述问题定方向】：挖掘需求锁定写作方向</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【基于目标定主题】：以终为始紧盯方案目标</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【纵向结构分层次】：换位思考解答对方困惑</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【横向结构选顺序】：梳理逻辑厘清表达思路</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">【形象表达做演示】：深入浅出传递关键信息</span></p>

4-1 描述问题定方向

